Search Functionality: Users can search for the current weather in any city.
Real-Time Data: The website fetches and displays up-to-date weather information.
Weather Details: Displays temperature, weather conditions, humidity, wind speed, and more.
Responsive Design: The website is fully responsive, ensuring it works well on both desktop and mobile devices.
Error Handling: Graceful handling of errors such as invalid city names or network issues.
Clean and Modern UI: A clean, modern, and intuitive user interface for a better user experience.
Technologies Used
Django: The main framework used for backend development.
HTML/CSS: For structuring and styling the web pages.
JavaScript: For enhancing user interactions and making asynchronous API calls.
Bootstrap: To ensure the website is responsive and has a modern look
